ANDROID_EPOCH_TIME.description: Current date and time, encoded as Epoch time (in milliseconds).

AP_POWER_BOOTUP_REASON.description: Property to report bootup reason for the current power on.

AP_POWER_STATE_REPORT.description: Property to report power state of application processor

AP_POWER_STATE_REQ.description: Property to control power state of application processor

CLUSTER_DISPLAY_STATE.description: Changes the state of the cluster display.

CLUSTER_REPORT_STATE.description: Reports the current display state and ClusterUI state.

CLUSTER_REQUEST_DISPLAY.description: Requests to change the cluster display state to show some ClusterUI.

CLUSTER_SWITCH_UI.description: Starts the ClusterUI in cluster display.

CREATE_USER.description: Called by the Android System after an Android user was created.

CURRENT_POWER_POLICY.description: Notifies the current power policy to VHAL layer.

DISABLED_OPTIONAL_FEATURES.description: Allow disabling optional featurs from vhal.

DISPLAY_BRIGHTNESS.description: Property to represent brightness of the display.

EV_BATTERY_INSTANTANEOUS_CHARGE_RATE.description: EV instantaneous charge rate in milliwatts

EV_BATTERY_LEVEL.description: EV battery level in WH, if EV or hybrid

EV_CHARGE_CURRENT_DRAW_LIMIT.description: Indicates the maximum current draw threshold for charging set by the user

EV_CHARGE_PERCENT_LIMIT.description: Indicates the maximum charge percent threshold set by the user

EV_CHARGE_SWITCH.description: Start or stop charging the EV battery

EV_CHARGE_TIME_REMAINING.description: Estimated charge time remaining in seconds

EV_REGENERATIVE_BRAKING_STATE.description: Regenerative braking or one-pedal drive state of the car

EXTERNAL_CAR_TIME.description: Current date and time suggestion for the Car, encoded as Epoch time (in milliseconds).

FUEL_LEVEL.description: Fuel remaining in the vehicle, in milliliters

HVAC_POWER_ON.description: Represents global power state for HVAC.

HVAC_TEMPERATURE_VALUE_SUGGESTION.description: Suggested values for setting HVAC temperature.

HW_CUSTOM_INPUT.description: Defines a custom OEM partner input event.

HW_KEY_INPUT.description: Property to feed H/W input events to android

HW_ROTARY_INPUT.description: Property to feed H/W rotary events to android

INFO_EV_BATTERY_CAPACITY.description: Battery capacity of the vehicle, if EV or hybrid.

INFO_EV_CONNECTOR_TYPE.description: List of connectors this EV may use

INFO_FUEL_CAPACITY.description: Fuel capacity of the vehicle in milliliters

INFO_FUEL_TYPE.description: List of fuels the vehicle may use

INITIAL_USER_INFO.description: Defines the initial Android user to be used during initialization.

PERF_ODOMETER.description: Current odometer value of the vehicle

PERF_REAR_STEERING_ANGLE.description: Rear bicycle model steering angle for vehicle

PERF_STEERING_ANGLE.description: Front bicycle model steering angle for vehicle

PERF_VEHICLE_SPEED_DISPLAY.description: Speed of the vehicle for displays

POWER_POLICY_GROUP_REQ.description: Defines a request to set the power polic group used to decide a default power policy per power status transition.

POWER_POLICY_REQ.description: Defines a request to apply power policy.

REMOVE_USER.description: Called by the Android System after an Android user was removed.

SUPPORT_CUSTOMIZE_VENDOR_PERMISSION.description: Support customize permissions for vendor properties

SWITCH_USER.description: Defines a request to switch the foreground Android user.

TRAILER_PRESENT.description: Indicates if there is a trailer present or not.

TURN_SIGNAL_STATE.description: State of the vehicles turn signals

USER_IDENTIFICATION_ASSOCIATION.description: Property used to associate (or query the association) the current user with vehicle-specific identification mechanisms (such as key FOB).

VHAL_HEARTBEAT.description: Defines an event that VHAL signals to car watchdog as a heartbeat.

WATCHDOG_ALIVE.description: Defines an event that car watchdog updates to tell it's alive.

WATCHDOG_TERMINATED_PROCESS.description: Defines a process terminated by car watchdog and the reason of termination.
